	<p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0374b25"/><lb ed="T" n="0374b25"/><persName key="A002250">釋法<ptr target="fn＊"/>珍</persName>，姓楊，<placeName key="PL000000005200">河東</placeName>人。少而好學，尋問萬里。<lb ed="T" n="0374b26"/><date key="j18755861876175" notAfter-iso="0424" notBefore-iso="0423">宋景平中</date>，來遊<placeName key="PL000000021526">兗</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000026339">豫</placeName>。貫極眾經，傍通異部。<lb ed="T" n="0374b27"/>後聽<placeName key="PL000000022347">東阿</placeName><persName key="A002229">靜公</persName>講，眾屢請覆述，<persName key="A002229">靜</persName>歎曰：「吾不<lb ed="T" n="0374b28"/>及也。」<date from-iso="0424" key="j18761761886925" to-iso="0454">元嘉中</date>中過江，<placeName key="PL000000012994">吳興</placeName><persName key="A003011">沈演之</persName>特深器重，<lb ed="T" n="0374b29"/>請還<placeName key="PL000000012994">吳興</placeName><placeName key="PL000000013052">武康小山寺</placeName>，首尾十有九年。自非<lb ed="T" n="0374c01"/>祈請法事，未嘗出門。居于<placeName key="PL000000013071">武康</placeName>，每歲開講，<lb ed="T" n="0374c02"/>三吳學者負笈盈衢。乃著《涅槃》、《法華》、《大品》、《勝<lb ed="T" n="0374c03"/>鬘》等義疏。<date key="j18898491890202" from-iso="0462-02-16" to-iso="0463-02-04">大明六年</date>，勅<placeName key="PL000000012994">吳興郡</placeName><ptr target="fn15"/>致禮上<placeName key="PL000000008976">京</placeName>，<lb ed="T" n="0374c04"/>與<persName key="A002251">道猷</persName>同止<placeName key="PL000000008701">新安寺</placeName>，使頓、漸二悟，義各有<lb ed="T" n="0374c05"/>宗。至便就講，鑾輿降蹕，百辟陪筵。<ptr target="fn＊"/><persName key="A002250">珍</persName>年<lb ed="T" n="0374c06"/>雖栖暮，而蔬苦弗改，戒節清白，道俗歸焉。<lb ed="T" n="0374c07"/><date key="j18938651895488" notAfter-iso="0477" notBefore-iso="0473">宋元徽中</date>卒，春秋七十有六。</p><p>時<placeName key="PL000000008758">宋熙</placeName>有<persName key="A003012">曇瑤</persName><lb ed="T" n="0374c08"/>者，善《淨名》、《十住》及《莊》、《老》，又工草隷，為<persName key="A003013">宋建<lb ed="T" n="0374c09"/>平宣簡王宏</persName>所重<ptr target="fn16"/>也。</p>
